gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 123, Lakers 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Lakers, 123-113. Grayson Allen recorded 24 points (6-12 3PM) and two rebounds for the Suns, with Jusuf Nurkic adding 18 points, 22 rebounds, and seven assists in the victory. LeBron James tallied 28 points, 12 assists, and seven rebounds for the Lakers in the loss. The Suns improve to 34-24, while the Lakers fall to 31-28.
